    <string name="txt_checkins_disables">\nFacebook is trying to access your location.\n
\nMost likely you are trying to \"Check-in\" to a specific place. While Tinfoil has optional permissions used for this, it is disabled by default.\n
\nYou can enable this feature by going to the Preferences and checking the option that says \"Allow Check-ins.\"\n
\nTinfoil only shares \"Coarse location\", this doesn\'t use the GPS, only Network and Wi-fi location in order to save battery.\n
\n</string>

